===================
What is TeensyKybd?
===================

If you're trying to determine what the hell this device is, please refer to http://wiki.github.com/mgoelzer/TeensyKybd/

==============
How to compile
==============

Type `make' in this directory.  

(You will need gcc-avr and so forth installed.  Refer to the Teensy documentation and examples to get the build environment set up.  The code is entirely C; no "Teensyduino" environment or libraries are needed.)

================
How to construct
================

The physical device can be built by wiring up the two boards as shown in the Kicad schematic.

